branchCategory.name: Rodless Cylinder - Magnetically Coupled - Low Profile Guide
branchCategory.description: <p>Rodless cylinder, magnetically coupled series CY*F type has a low profile for applications tight on space. Magnetically coupled cylinders have a wide range of applications, and save mounting space. Loads and moments are possible through the use of integrated guides. </p>

breadCrumb.name: Rodless Cylinder - Magnetically Coupled - Low Profile Guide

branchItem.name: Rodless Cylinder, CY1F, Magnetically Coupled - Low Profile Guide
branchItem.description: <p>The CY1F low profile Rodless Cylinder - Magnetically Coupled uses industrial strength magnets located in the piston and external carriage to form a single unit that will travel when actuated with air pressure. It is installed with a single axis internal linear guide to reduce its profile as much as 29% and up to 50% weight reduction compared to the CY1H Series.</p>
